item.description:
Please join me for some easy Disc golf. If this is new to you, come try it and have some fun. We toss frisbees at metal baskets out on wooded trails. It's a great way to get some fresh air and excersize :).
We will meet at the store across from the park to pick up the free discs then head to the park. Were usually there 2-3 hours. Bring water, sunscreen and bug spray. Also good shoes as we will be out walking thru the woods. If we decide to eat after, there is a nice sandwich counter at the store.
Questions 603-315-0275
Cindy
item.how_to_find_us: We will meet at the store across from the park to pick up discs
item.name: Wimp Disc Golf
